Cutar coronavirus mai yaduwa (COVID-19) a Majalisar Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Turai da Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Cutar coronavirus mai kama da juna (COVID-19) tana nuna mummunan yaduwa kamar a cikin Tarayyar Turai / Hukumar Tsaro ta Turai da Majalisar Dinkin Duniya da ke fama da cutar, kuma a wasu lokuta, cutar COVID-19 tana yaduwa cikin sauri a duk faɗin duniya.
Idan har aka ci gaba da wannan lamarin a Italiya, jihohi, asibitoci da kungiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya za su kara shirin su don yawan masu cutar COVID-19 da za a kula da su a cikin jiki, da kuma kula da marasa lafiya.
A ranar 31 ga watan Disamba na 2019, an samu wani kwayar cutar sankarar bargo da ba a san ko ta wane suna ba a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, kasar Sin.
A ranar 9 ga watan Janairun 2020, Hukumar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta bayyana cewa sabon kwayar cutar coronavirus da aka sani da cutar sankarar barbashi mai saurin yaduwa ta 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ne ya haifar da cutar.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da SARS-CoV ta haifar ta zama sanannen cuta (COVI-19).
Bayanai sun nuna cewa kusan kashi 80% na mutanen da suka mutu suna da mummunan cututtuka, kamar su cututtukan da ke shafar numfashi, da kuma ciwon sukari.
A cikin kashi 14% na masu cutar, COVID-19 yana haifar da rashin lafiya da ke haifar da rashin lafiya da ke haifar da asibiti da kuma kashi 6% na marasa lafiya suna fama da rashin lafiya da ke buƙatar kulawa ta likita.
Mutuwar marasa lafiya da ke cikin asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kashi 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken, muna nazarin yanayin barkewar cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta Tarayyar Turai / EEA da Ƙasar Ingila (UK) da ke lardin Hubei, China.
Har ila yau, na ci gaba da lura da yawan adadin masu cutar COVID-19 a yanzu a cikin EU/EEA da UK da waɗanda suka kasance a Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK
Bayan China, COVID-19 ta mamaye wasu yankuna kuma sauran ƙasashen duniya suna bin sahun COVID-19.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Babban Jami'in Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin cutar ta duniya.
A cikin fitowar Eurosurveillance na 5 ga Maris, 2020, Spiteri al. ya ba da rahoton farkon ainihin cutar COVID-19 a Turai kamar yadda WHO ta bayyana.
A cikin EU/EEA, an fara rahoton wasu cututtukan uku daga Faransa a ranar 24 ga Janairun 2020 a cikin mutanen da ke birnin Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano wasu cututtukan COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashe 30 na EU/EEA da na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda a tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 da kuma yanzu an sami sabbin kamuwa da cutar 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727 da kuma mutuwar 1,441 a Italiya.
Samun cikakken bayani game da adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19
A Hukumar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), yawan adadin masu cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda ke ba da tabbacin ga masu ba da tabbaci kamar su Shugabannin Hukumar Lafiya, shugabannin jihohi da na birni da WHO za a bincika a kowace rana da karfe 8:00 na yamma.
Ana amfani da wannan bayanin don gwajin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK, kuma ana gwada shi da na Italiya.
A matsayin nazarin yawan masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19, mun lissafa yawan adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19, yayin da muke lissafin yanayin COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da kuma a cikin Burtaniya daga ranar 1 ga Janairu zuwa ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Mun kuma nuna jimlar adadin masu cutar da aka ruwaito a kowace ƙasa a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da karfe 8:00 na yamma a nan Italiya daga ranar 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK.
Ci gaban da aka samu a cikin jerin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA a cikin kwanaki 14 da suka gabata da kuma Burtaniya sun biyo bayan na lardin Hubei (China) (Hoto 1).
Dangane da EU/EEA da UK baki ɗaya, yawan adadin masu cutar COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa daga ranar 21 ga Fabrairu zuwa 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (Wasu bayanai).
Mafi yawan abin da ya haifar da wannan shine ƙarancin adadin masu cutar da aka ruwaito a Italiya, yayin da sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK ke nuna irin wannan ci gaban a cikin adadin COVID-19 (Wasu abubuwa).
Hoto na 2 ya nuna kwatancen adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19, a cikin EU/EEA da UK a cikin adadin da aka samu a Italiya a lokacin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Ya ce, a ranar 15 ga Maris da karfe 8:00 na yamma, wasu kasashe 15 na EU/EEA da UK sun ba da rahoton adadin masu cutar da za a iya ganowa kamar na Italiya a cikin kwanaki 3 kafin ko bayan karshen.
A cewar rahotanni, yawan adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 da aka ruwaito ya yi kasa da na EU/EEA da UK.
Sakamakon binciken da muke yi game da yaduwar COVID-19 ya nuna cewa cutar tana da alaƙa da alamun da za a iya magance su a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan saboda ƙasashe masu tasowa, canje-canje a cikin yarda da kula da lafiyar ƙasa, da kuma bambancin yanayin ƙasa da kuma wasu hanyoyin da za a zaɓi waɗanda za su sake yin gwajin COVID-19, da kuma ƙarin gwaji.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da ke fama da cutar a Italiya sun tabbatar da cewa kashi 10 cikin dari na masu cutar COVID-19 suna bukatar kulawa ta musamman kuma rahotanni sun nuna cewa asibitoci da kungiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya a yankunan ba su cika wannan burin ba.
Rahoton cutar COVID-19 a asibiti da/ko cibiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya yana cikin EU/EEA na 6% da 1% na masu cutar, bi da bi (wanda zai nuna bayanai).
Bayan haka, za a tattara su cikin wani sashi don samar da bayanan kulawa da ke tattare da yawan adadin cututtuka da mutuwar.
Wani bincike a cikin 2010-2011 ya nuna bambancin yanayin da ke cikin wuraren zama da kuma umarnin kulawa da marasa lafiya a Turai, daga 29.2 gadaje a Jamus zuwa 4.2 ga mutane 100,000 a Portugal.
A cewar rahotanni, ƙasashen na iya samun talauci fiye da Italiya (12.5 mafi yawan gadajen jinya da kuma kula da lafiya ga kowane mutum 100,000 a 2010-11).
Shirya jadawalin da ke tattare da tsarin karɓar baƙi, da kuma yiwuwar kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya ta karɓi marasa lafiya na COVID-19 waɗanda ke buƙatar asibiti da kuma waɗanda ke buƙatar gado waɗanda ke buƙatar samun umarnin kula da mutum aƙalla kashi 90% na jerin abubuwan da ke cikin takardar shaidar bincike na ECDC don gwajin cutar COVID-19.
Saboda karuwar cututtuka a wasu sassan EU/EEA da UK, da kuma asibitoci da kungiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya da ke aiki a wuraren da ke da matukar dacewa ga marasa lafiya, za a iya samun bayanai game da cututtukan da ke da gado a kowane birni na lardin 2 (NUTS-2).
Abubuwan da suka faru a Italiya da kuma halin da ake ciki a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa cutar COVID-19 tana gudana a cikin EU/EEA da UK.
Kasashe, cibiyoyi da kungiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya dole ne su tsara yadda za su taimaka wa jama'a don magance SARS-CoV-2 da kuma karuwar adadin masu cutar COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa ta musamman, kamar waɗanda ke faruwa a yankunan da ke cikin Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka lissafa a cikin binciken cutar ta ECDC, akwai cikakkiyar hanyar da za a bi don hana yaduwar SARS-COV-2, tare da hanyar da za ta iya motsawa daga magani zuwa raguwa, kamar yadda yawan masu cutar da ke ci gaba da ƙaruwa ba zai ba masu ɗaukar hoto damar fahimtar, amsawa da kuma magance matsalar su ba.
Binciken cututtukan cututtuka na yau da kullun yana ƙididdige matakan kula da lafiyar gwamnati don rage tasirin cutar.
Akwai yiwuwar yiwuwar cewa ƙasashe za su iya samun hanyoyin da za su iya haɓaka ƙarfin su wajen rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage saurin kula da lafiya.
Idan hakan ta faru, to ana iya ganin cewa tsarin kula da lafiya na wasu kasashen EU/EEA zai sami matsala saboda yawan masu bukatar kulawar da ke faruwa a wasu kasashen zai karu a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wadda kwayar cutar sankarar bargo (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ke haifarwa, ta kuma kashe mutane sama da 3,000 tare da kamuwa da fiye da 80,000 a China da sauran sassan duniya, wanda hakan ya zama wata babbar matsalar al'umma.
Kamar yadda yake a cikin cutar SARS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da SARS a cikin dubban mutane a 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya zama mai yaduwa daga kwari kuma yana haifar da alamun cutar ta hanyar irin wannan cutar.
Koyaya, COVID-19 ya fi kisa da rashin lafiya fiye da SARS kuma yana da saurin kamuwa da cuta kuma yana shafar tsofaffi fiye da masu kulawa da maza fiye da mata.
Don magance yawan masu cutar da ke haifar da cutar, wannan rahoton ya yi watsi da bayar da bincike a kan lokaci da kuma bambancin da aka yi a cikin binciken.
Za mu kuma tattauna game da ilimin kamuwa da cuta, rigakafin cutar, ilimin kwayar cuta, ganewar asali, magani, tsinkaya, da kuma rigakafin cutar.
Duk da cewa akwai wasu maganganu da yawa da za su iya amsawa, muna tsammanin wannan bayanin yana da mahimmanci a fahimtar da kuma magance matsalar.
Bikin bazara na ranar 25 ga Janairun 2020 ya zama abin tunawa ga duk Sinawa da ke cikin gida a duk lokacin hutu da kuma mako-mako saboda sabon cutar.
Kwayar cutar ta yi kama da kwayar cutar coronavirus (CoV) wacce ta haifar da cutar sankarar barbashi mai saurin kamuwa da cuta (SARS) a shekarar 2003; saboda haka Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta sake sanya wa SARS-CoV-2 suna, kuma an sake kiran cutar da cutar COVID-19 (COVID-19).
Cutar ta fara ne a Wuhan, kasar Sin, daga baya ta yadu zuwa kasar baki daya kuma ta kai kusan kasashe 50 a duniya.
Tun daga ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, cutar ta kamu da mutane 80,000 da aka sani da cutar COVID-19, tare da 40,000 da ke warkewa da sama da 3,000 da suka mutu.
WHO ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 "mafi munin cuta ga dan adam" kuma yana iya zama mafi muni.
A cewar wani rahoto a PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed), kafin a buga shi a cikin watanni biyu, an buga takardu sama da 200 game da COVID-19 da ilimin kwayoyin cutar, allurar rigakafi, bincike, da magani tun farkon fitowar ta a ranar 7 ga Janairu 2020 wanda ya nuna cewa kwayoyin sun bambanta a cikin yawancin marasa lafiya.
Wannan bincike yana nufin samar da cibiyar bincike a cikin sabon ilmantarwa da sauri.
A wani bangare, za mu tattauna game da annobar COVID-19 da SARS da kuma wata annoba, wato, cutar murar tsakiya ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS, wata annoba ta 2012).
Muna kuma fatan cewa za mu tattauna abin da muka koya game da rigakafi da kuma tsammanin cututtuka da kuma abubuwan da ke faruwa a yanzu.
CoVs suna kama da tsutsotsi waɗanda ba sa kashe mutane kamar yadda suka saba, suna haifar da mura a kashi 15% na cututtukan 4.
A wannan yanayin, duk da haka, zamu iya cewa wasu CoVs masu cutarwa sun kamu da cutar sau biyu, kamar su, SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, wanda ya fara yaduwa a China a 2003 da Larabawa a 2012, kuma daga baya ya isa wasu ƙasashe tare da yawan adadin kamuwa da cuta.
Bugu da ƙari, cutar COVID-19 ta yanzu ita ce ta uku a tarihin ɗan adam.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a hoto, hoto na 1.1, an samu wani sabon kamuwa da cutar sankarar bargo a Wuhan a ranar 31 ga watan Disambar 2019 a Hukumar Lafiya ta kasar Sin.
Bayan kwanaki shida da rabi, cutar CoV ta fito.
A ranar 15 ga Janairun 2020, mutum na farko ya mutu a Wuhan.
A wannan lokacin, cutar ta fara yaduwa zuwa birane, larduna, da ƙasashe.
A ranar 20 ga watan Janairu, an bayar da rahoton cewa an samu wasu mutane da suka kamu da cutar, amma ba a tabbatar da yiwuwar cutar ta yadu daga mutum zuwa mutum ba.
Tun daga ranar 23 ga Janairun 2020, an rufe birnin Wuhan kuma an dakatar da duk zirga-zirgar jiragen sama.
A ranar 24 ga watan Janairun, binciken farko na binciken da aka yi a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje ya nuna cewa, daga cikin mutane 41 da suka kamu da cutar, 21 sun kamu da cutar Wuhan, wanda ake ganin ya haifar da cutar daga wata kwayar halitta da ba a sani ba.
Bayan ranar 30 ga watan Janairun, WHO ta ayyana dokar ta baci ta kiwon lafiya a duniya.
A lokacin da aka rubuta wannan labarin, an riga an kawar da cutar a China da kuma kusan ƙasashe 50 a duniya (Hoto (Hoto 2).).
Ko da yake cutar tana ci gaba, ƙarshen rashin lafiya ko rashin lafiya zai iya zama mai ban mamaki.
A ranar 11 ga Fabrairun 2020, an yi nazarin mutane 8,866 da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 kuma an kammala bincike kan mutane 4,021 a cikin dakunan gwaje-gwaje daban-daban don gano sabon cutar kamar haka (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UIBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 yana kamuwa da mutane na kowane zamani, musamman waɗanda shekarunsu suka kai 30 zuwa 65.
Kusan rabin (47.7%) na waɗanda ke fama da cutar sun fi shekaru 50, waɗanda ba su kai shekara 20 ba ba su da yawa, kuma kusan 14 cikin mutane da ke fama da cutar sun kai shekaru 10.
SARS-CoV-2 ya kamu da maza da yawa (0.31/100,000) fiye da mata (0.27/100,000).
COVID-19 ya bazu a cikin iska da kuma wurare masu zafi a Hubei da yammacin yamma.
COVID-19 yana ɗaukar kwanaki 5 (2 zuwa 9) daga farkon gwajin.
Lokacin da aka bayyana shine kimanin kwanaki 4.8 (3.0 zuwa 7.2).
Lokacin da ya kamata daga farkon zuwa ƙarshen shine kimanin kwanaki 9.5 (4.8 zuwa 13).
Sakamakon farko na haihuwa (R0) shine 3.77 (95% CI:3.51-4.05), kuma R0 da aka gwada shine 2.23-4.82.
Yawan masu kamuwa da cutar zai iya zama mafi girma kafin ranar 23 ga Janairun 2020, wanda ya dace da lokacin da aka dakatar da zirga-zirga kafin bikin bazara a China.
Mutuwar cututtukan da aka gano sun kasance 1.44% (59% CI:1.10-1.86%), kuma yawan mutuwar da aka gano ya kasance 3.06% (95% CI: 2.02-4.59%).
Abubuwa uku da ke haifar da kamuwa da COVID-19 sune tsufa (shekarun da suka gabata), shekaru (≥60), da kuma ciwon zuciya mai tsanani.
Kwayoyin cuta na CoV suna kama da rukuni na kwayoyin cuta da ƙwayoyin cuta da ke da ƙwayoyin RNA guda ɗaya.
Ana iya rarraba shi zuwa rukuni huɗu, wato, alpha, beta, gamma, delta, da cov alpha da beta kamar yadda suke shafar mutane.
Bayan ƙwayar (S) glycoprotein yana haɗuwa da mai karɓar mai karɓar angiotensin kuma yana mayar da kwayoyin 2 (ACE2) da dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4) don SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, daban, da kuma haɗuwa.
Kwayar RNA ta kwayar cutar ta shiga cikin cytoplasm; bayan an haifi kwayar halitta, kwayar RNA ta kwayar halitta da glycoproteins da nucleocapsid suna dauke da ƙananan ƙwayoyin cuta da ke karɓar kwayoyin cutar, wanda ke shiga cikin jini kuma yana haɗuwa da ƙwayar cutar.
An fara rahoton cutar SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 10 ga Janairun 2020.
An gano SARS-CoV-2 a matsayin sabon beta-CoV wanda ya fi ingancin kwayoyin halitta 99.98% a cikin samfuran 10 da aka ɗauka a farkon farkon barkewar cutar, Kasuwar Abinci ta Kifi ta Huanan a Wuhan.
SARS-CoV-2 yana da kamanceceniya ta kwayoyin halitta da SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV.
